author: Crystal Bell
title: Jordan Fisher Is The Internet’s Most Self-Aware Boyfriend
description: Jordan Fisher is known as the internet's wholesome new boyfriend. Here, the 'Dear Evan Hansen' star and songwriter talks about keeping himself busy with gaming and anime, choosing happiness, and how his perfectionism is his worst habit.
